snippet.title: Mister Viking [Arcade Longplay] (1984) Sega {315-5041, Japan}
snippet.description: Full playthrough of the arcade game Mister Viking. Horizontal shoot'em up game with Vikings theme. Released back in 1984 by Sega. Japan version of the game, 315-5041.
